---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="アクセス" description="イーエントリー株式会社へのアクセス方法、所在地、最寄駅からの道順をご案内します">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>アクセス</h1>
      <p>イーエントリー株式会社へのアクセス</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="access-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="access-grid">
        <div class="company-info-card">
          <h2>所在地</h2>
          <div class="info-content">
            <div class="info-item">
              <div class="info-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="info-text">
                <p class="label">住所</p>
                <p class="address">
                  〒106-0032<br>
                  東京都港区六本木1-3-38<br>
                  アークタワーズサウス S204
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-item">
              <div class="info-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
                  <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"/>
                  <line x1="15" y1="3" x2="15" y2="21"/>
                  <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/>
                  <line x1="3" y1="15" x2="21" y2="15"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="info-text">
                <p class="label">最寄駅</p>
                <p>東京メトロ南北線<br>六本木一丁目駅 徒歩3分</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="map-container">
          <h2>周辺地図</h2>
          <div class="map-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/access/map-area.gif" alt="周辺地図" class="map-image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="directions-map">
        <h2>最寄駅からの道順</h2>
        <p class="directions-subtitle">東京メトロ南北線 六本木一丁目駅から徒歩3分</p>
        <div class="map-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/access/map-route.gif" alt="最寄駅からの道順" class="map-image">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="directions-section">
        <h2>詳しい道順</h2>
        
        <div class="steps-grid">
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>改札を出る</h3>
              <p>改札口を出てすぐの番号のない出口を出る。「泉ガーデンレジデンス」への赤い看板が目印。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>エスカレーターを上がる</h3>
              <p>屋外のエスカレーターを4つ上がり、突き当りを左へ曲がる。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>道路に出る</h3>
              <p>泉ガーデンレジデンスのエントランス前を抜けて道路に出て、左へ道なりに進む。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>到着</h3>
              <p>青いＰの看板のある6階建て住居ビル。赤いポスト横の階段を上がると入口。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-note">
        <div class="note-content">
          <div class="note-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M12 16v-4"/>
              <path d="M12 8h.01"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="note-text">
            <h3>ご来社の際は</h3>
            <p>ご来社いただく際は、事前にお問い合わせフォームまたはお電話にてご連絡をお願いいたします。</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">お問い合わせ</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 70px;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0066ff 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .access-section {
    padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .access-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .company-info-card {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    height: fit-content;
  }

  .company-info-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .info-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .info-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .info-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .info-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .address {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-text p:not(.label) {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .map-container h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .map-wrapper {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .map-wrapper:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .map-wrapper iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .map-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 12px;
    max-height: 500px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .directions-map {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .directions-map h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .directions-map .map-wrapper {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .directions-map .map-image {
    max-height: 600px;
  }

  .directions-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .directions-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .directions-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .step-card {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .step-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0066ff 100%);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .step-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0066ff 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-note {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .note-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .note-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .note-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .note-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .note-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .note-text p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0066ff 100%);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .access-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .map-wrapper {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .access-section {
      padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .access-grid {
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .company-info-card,
    .step-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .directions-section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .contact-note {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .note-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .note-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .map-wrapper iframe {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .map-image {
      max-height: 300px;
    }

    .directions-map .map-image {
      max-height: 400px;
    }
  }
</style>